The '''Academy of Drama and Film in Budapest''' is a [[university]] founded in 1865 in [[Budapest]], [[Hungary]]. The institution became a university in 2000 and the name has changed to '''University of Theatre and Film Arts'''.<ref>{{cite web|title=University of Theatre and Film Arts, Budapest|url=http://szfe.hu/en/participating-universities/university-theatre-film-arts-budapest/|publisher=szfe.hu|accessdate=30 March 2017}}</ref>
